data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this inviting 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom Syracuse home, peacefully situated on Woods Rd. Step inside to a spacious living area with plenty of room to relax and entertain. The kitchen boasts updated appliances and ample cabinet space, making meal preparation a breeze. You'll appreciate the cozy bedrooms for a good night's rest, and the well-appointed bathroom offers both style and function. The backyard provides a serene retreat, perfect for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the fresh air. With its charming appeal and desirable location, this home presents a unique opportunity to make it your own. Don't miss out on this gem!
